Posts.Content: I had my mammogram yesterday and today I got a call from my Doctor. All he said wsa I needed to go have an ultra sound because there is somthing showing up on my lymph nodes? Of course it was 5 pm and I can't find out anything till morning. I have always heard Lymph nodes was not good. Can anyone give me any advice. I am in a real panic. Any advice is much thanked. Marti
